<i>adverb</i>: 터무니없이 [터무니업씨], 생판 [생판], 생으로 [생으로], 물색없이 [물쌔겁씨] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>터무니없이 [터무니업씨]</dt><br>
<dd>absurdly; unreasonably</dd><br>
<dd>황당하고 믿음성이 없어 전혀 근거가 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without a foundation, as something is ridiculous and lacks credibility.</dd><br>
<dt>생판 [생판]</dt><br>
<dd>1. utterly; totally</dd><br>
<dd>아주 낯설게. 또는 아무 상관없게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a very unfamiliar manner, or in a completely irrelevant manner.</dd><br>
<dd>2. groundlessly; unreasonably; unjustly</dd><br>
<dd>매우 황당하고 이치에 맞지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a very absurd and unreasonable manner.</dd><br>
<dt>생으로 [생으로]</dt><br>
<dd>1. in the raw</dd><br>
<dd>익거나 마르지 않은 날것 그대로.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being raw and not cooked or dried.</dd><br>
<dd>2. forcibly; unreasonably</dd><br>
<dd>그럴 만한 상황이 아닌데도 무리하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being unreasonable, disregarding the situation.</dd><br>
<dd>3. painfully hard</dd><br>
<dd>아무런 처리나 도움 없이 몹시 힘들게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner that one suffers extremely without receiving treatment or help.</dd><br>
<dt>물색없이 [물쌔겁씨]</dt><br>
<dd>unreasonably; abruptly</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동이 형편에 어울리지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner that one's speaking or behavior is not suitable for a particular situation.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>